data.description: Newly built in 2020 this beautifully finished and well maintained townhome is located in the private waterfront community of Shaws Discovery. Just 15 minutes from downtown Baltimore!  This 3 bedroom home nestled in the back of the community features an oversized driveway with attached 1 car garage, open concept main level, large living area flowing into the kitchen with elegant white cabinetry, granite counters, true pantry, oversized island with seating space and gorgeous floors throughout. Sliding glass door leads from the dining room to the rear deck with views of Back River.  Stunning primary bedroom with elegant tray ceilings, generous size walk in closet, double vanity bath and walk-in dual shower. Upstairs complete with 2 additional bedrooms, full bath and laundry located conveniently in hall.   Additional living area on the lower level perfect for whatever extra space is needed, game room, home theater, gym, office, endless possibilities!  Loads of community amenities such as walking paths, boat ramp and a private pavilion just to name a few!
